text.tspan: Based on the expert assessments and index by V-Dem, weighted by countries' populations. It combines information on
voting rights, the freedom and fairness of elections, freedoms of association and expression, as well as the extent to
which citizens and leaders discuss different views and seek the public good. It ranges from 0 to 1 (most democratic).
Data source: OWID based on V-Dem (v13)
